tourBios.carHigh:
Is a multiple winner on the PGA Venezuela .

2012: Was T4 at the International Open La Vitalicia in Venezuela, allowing him to finish 16th on the Tour de las Américas Order of Merit. This meant he earned the 10th and last spot available for the best Tour de las Américas players not already exempt to play on the PGA TOUR Latinoamérica.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Was the Venezuela amateur champion in 2002.
tourBios.personal: Has a degree in business administration and law practice.

dyn.dynResults: He has finished 17th on the PGA TOUR Latinoameri 2 times.
